
Demonstration Steps
Step 1

Login to the ServiceNow instance.

Step 2

Open the Service Portal or Service Catalog.

Step 3

Submit a Network Request by entering the required details.

Step 4

Observe the automated approval workflow.

Step 5

Approve or reject the request.

Step 6

Verify automatic task creation.

Step 7

Complete the assigned fulfillment task.

Step 8

Monitor automatic status updates.

Step 9

View reports and dashboards.

Expected Result
Request successfully submitted.
Approval process executed automatically.
Task assigned to the network team.
Notifications sent to users.
Request completed with real-time status tracking.
Reports updated automatically.
